{"thag2.2:0.1":"Theragatha 2.2 ","thag2.2:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag2.2:0.4":"Pindolabharadvajattheragatha ","thag2.2:1.1":"“Nayidam anayena jivitam, ","thag2.2:1.2":"Naharo hadayassa santiko; ","thag2.2:1.3":"Aharatthitiko samussayo, ","thag2.2:1.4":"Iti disvana carami esanam. ","thag2.2:2.1":"Pankoti hi nam pavedayum, ","thag2.2:2.2":"Yayam vandanapujana kulesu; ","thag2.2:2.3":"Sukhumam sallam durubbaham, ","thag2.2:2.4":"Sakkaro kapurisena dujjaho”ti. ","thag2.2:2.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma pindolabharadvajo thero gathayo abhasitthati. "}